        <num>CC 2894</num>
        <heading>2894.  Preservation and limited use</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2894.  Preservation and limited use
The borrower is bound to keep, preserve, and use the thing lent as a prudent administrator.  He may use it only according to its nature or as provided in the contract.</p>
        </content>
